Description:
SPACIOUS PARK FRONT LIVING!
Ideally located directly fronting parkland this spacious home has so much to offer. A clever floor plan of 4 bedrooms (main with WIR & full ensuite). Two separate living areas including formal lounge & a large open plan kitchen/meals/living area with split system cooling. The kitchen boasts stainless appliances including dishwasher and an abundance of cupboard & bench space.
Features include gas ducted heating, split system cooling, double lock-up garage with internal access and a private courtyard.
Note: This property is currently leased at $1564 pcm on a periodic tenancy with a fabulous tenant who would love to stay if you're wanting a ready to go investment!
Photo ID is required at all inspections.

Description:
UNDER CONTRACT/ UNDER OFFER!
Cranbourne East-:Why go through the hassle of building when you have 25 Artfield Street just waiting for you?
Requiring an estate offering family friendly living? Wanting to be within a brief distance to major shopping facilities and freeway access? And walking distance to a great park? Then is home is the perfect solution for you!
Situated amongst quality homes is this outstanding opportunity within an affordable price bracket. Ideal for First Home Buyers, empty nesters and any astute investors looking to profit from the high depreciation potential on offer!
This quality built property features 4 bedrooms. The master is complete with full ensuite with WIR, 2nd & 3rd are both good sizes with BIRs and are conveniently positioned close to the family bathroom with separate toilet facilities and the 4th bedroom is doubled up as a home office/ study and. The kitchen provides a great size bench space, plenty of cupboard space, stainless steel under bench oven, stainless steel cooktop, rangehood and microwave provision & all of this overlooks the large, open family/meals zone with external sliding door access to the backyard.
Added internal extras include, wider halls and door, Double Glaze windows, high quality carpet and curtains/ blinds, ducted heating, 5X S/S Air cons, convenient blend of tiles & carpet throughout, internal access from the remote double garage
Outside you will be greeted by a low maintenance, but yet great size front and backyard. Under roof alfresco with decking and lighting, concrete paths and Colourbond fencing.
Within a short drive to freeway access and all amenities located in the townships of Berwick, Clyde and Cranbourne this sensational opportunity is only minutes away from the popular Clyde Primary School, Casey RACE Recreation & Aquatic Centre and Casey Indoor Sports Centre! With additional shopping precincts in Pasadena, Selandra Rise/Cascades on Clyde and The Hunt Club local amenities are always going to be close by, whilst the recently revamped Cranbourne Park Shopping Centre offers an abundance of cafes and restaurants! Don't forget the proposed Cranbourne East train station, or the existing ones situated right throughout the South East!
If you want your family to have easy access to the very best in entertainment, education and recreation call today before it's selling, selling ..... SOLD!
*PHOTO ID REQUIRED AT OPEN FOR INSPECTIONS*!
At Ray White Cranbourne our price indications are based upon probable market value, the likely selling price and the vendor's expectations. You can view with confidence that vendors will sell within the range with favourable conditions.
Our floor plans are for representational purposes only and should be used as such. We accept no liability for the accuracy or details contained in our floor plans

Description:
UNDER CONTRACT
Situated in the highly sort after Cascades on Clyde sits this well presented three bedroom home.
The estate has lots to offer with easy access to Selandra Rise shops which includes Safeway, Cafes, Takeaway food shops aswell as a Dog park, Lots of walking tracks, Bus stop, Childcare centre, Gym, Schools and much more.
The home features open plan living with light filled family meals area which opens to an undercover alfresco for all year round entertaining.
Kitchen with abundance of storage, stainless steel appliances including dishwasher, oven/cooktop and rangehood.
Master bedroom with double built in robes and full ensuite.
Remaining bedrooms all with built in robes.
Main bathroom and seperate toilet.
Garage situated at the rear of the property with access via lane way.
Other featured inclusions are gas ducted heating, split system cooling, fibre optic connections for fast internet and and a low maintenance yard.
The property sits on 320sq metres of land and is only seven years young so if you are looking to buy your first home, down size or invest this property certainly ticks all the boxes.
Currently tenanted at $360.00 per week / $1560.00 per month.
For any enquiries please call Hayley on 0488 049 143 or email info@allaboutsales.com.au

Description:
HOME IS WHERE YOUR HEART IS, RIGHT HERE IN CRANBOURNE EAST
CRANBOURNE EAST - Neat as a pin home on a flat and functional 649 sqm block comprising a solid 3 bed, 1 bath, DLUG brick veneer home and waiting for the astute purchaser. Investor? First home buyer? Renovator? Developer? - come one, come all! With plenty of land to do with what you please, a great neighbourhood, close to all amenities, local park lands, public transport, schools all nearby, you would be crazy to miss out on this opportunity. The house has been home to the current tenant for the past nine years! They have cared for this home as if it were their own, and this is reflected in the overall condition of the property. As an investor, you can't go past a great tenant with an established history. As a new home owner, you have a blank canvas to create your own piece of suburban paradise in a peaceful area fully supported by a growing community. Three good sized bedrooms all with BIRs, family bathroom, large open plan kitchen meals and separate formal living area. Ducted heating, D/W, GHWS, Gas cooking, DLUG with direct entry to the large open backyard with plenty of space for a boat, caravan, or perhaps another dwelling or extend the existing home. So many choices, so many options! This home is a great buy in a well sought after location!
CRANBOURNE EAST
Cranbourne East is located on the outskirts of Cranbourne Central. The area offers Cranbourne East Primary and Cranbourne East Secondary College as well as Cranbourne Secondary College and is surrounded by multiple Shopping Centres. Also located nearby is the newly constructed Casey Fields football ground, Casey Race Recreation & Aquatic Centre, and Casey Library.

Description:
Family Parkside Living
Four bedrooms, four bathrooms and only five years old, this beautiful family home, designed and constructed by Carlisle Homes has loads to offer including two storeys of spacious modern living, a wonderful park side position and approximately two years of builder warranty remaining. A fantastic family gem perfect for big, growing and extended families.
Both spacious and elegant, this home offers four living zones, four bedrooms plus a study or fifth bedroom and an outdoor alfresco living area. Enter through double doors into the grand entrance hall and you will be immediately impressed by the spacious interiors, luxurious finishes and timeless colour palette.
The layout begins with a formal lounge perfect for entertaining and a conveniently located study(or fifth bedroom). Across the hall is a brilliant theatre room, ideal for amusing the kids, enjoying family movies together or a quiet date night in. Continue through to the open plan kitchen, meals and family area; where the hostess's kitchen is beautifully appointed with stone benchtops, stainless steel appliances, including a five burner gas cooktop, 900mm electric oven and dishwasher as well as plenty of storage and bench space. Complimented by a walk-in pantry with additional sink. This kitchen is a dream for any home-cook, hostess or budding chef! The adjoining meals and family room create the perfect setup for social living and they also enjoy a connection to the alfresco area and views onto the rear yard.
Upstairs is a large versatile living space with private balcony overlooking the park. The lavish master suite provides a spacious bedroom with his and hers walk-in robes and a modern en-suite with oversized shower and bath, double vanity and a separate toilet. The three remaining bedrooms all include walk in robes and individual en-suites.
Other features of the home include ducted heating and evaporative cooling throughout, an alarm system and high ceilings. This modern home is completed with a low maintenance front and rear yard, double garage with additional rear roller door access and lovely views over the adjacent parkland.
This superb property is located close to Cranbourne East Primary School and St Thomas Primary School, as well as the Cranbourne High Street shops and the many recreational facilities at Casey Fields Sporting Complex plus easy access to the South Gippsland Highway.
Beautifully styled and designed to cater for every aspect of family living, this home truly has everything you could ask for. Call now to snap up this wonderful opportunity.

This impressive property features 4 large bedrooms, the master includes a walk in robe and full ensuite, second & third bedrooms also with Built in robes that are conveniently serviced by the sleek central bathroom. Formal lounge room, stunning kitchen with white stone tops benches, tiled splash-back, quality stainless steel appliances and a massive walk in pantry overlook the spacious open plan family and meals area. In addition you will find a separate laundry with external access and double car garage with internal access.
Outside your spoilt for space and have room to move within the private low maintenance rear yard, landscaped gardens and an impressive covered concreted alfresco area, which is perfect for all weather entertaining.
This property is fitted with quality floating floorboards, premium carpets and tiles. Keep comfortable all year round with ducted heating and evaporative cooling.
Located just off Linsell Boulevard and a stone's throw away from a range of parks, sporting facilities, schools, child care centres and shops, this home is the perfect fit.

PRIME PORTER DAVIS
Situated in the Livingstone Estate is this attractive rendered Porter Davis built 2 storey home boasting; 4 bedrooms plus study.

- Open plan lounge dining off the kitchen with access to a lovely alfresco area.
- 2 spacious bathrooms including full en-suite with large shower plus a downstairs powder room (3rd toilet)
- There is evaporative cooling, gas ducted heating, quality tiles and carpets plus double lock up garage with internal access all on a low maintenance allotment.
The location is ideal as its within close proximity of the Aquatic Centre, Casey Fields, local shops and schools & just a short drive to Cranbourne's main shopping precinct.

Description:
A stone's throw away from the shops
Located in the HUNT CLUB, one of the most sort after estates of Cranbourne East is this beautiful award winning design family home.
The fantastic property features 3 spacious bedrooms, master with full ensuite and walk in robe, whilst the remaining 2 bedrooms have built in robes and are conveniently positioned around the second bathroom.
The kitchen has ample bench and cupboard space, dishwasher and quality appliances. It's centrally positioned and has an open and inviting feel, overlooking the huge separate dining area, perfect for dinner parties!
The two separate living areas provides enough room for both parents and kids, with a spacious front formal lounge and informal family area with access to the patio.
Outside, low maintenance gardens back and front.
The large paved area is ideal for summer lunches and BBQ'S with friends and family.
Added extras include; gas heating, air con, down lights, feature walls and double remote garage with internal access.
A fantastic location within seconds walk to the Hunt Club shopping village, Wetlands, walking/bicycle paths, childcare, primary and secondary schools and public transport.
Avoid the disappointment of missing out and call MINA on 0401 053 553 to arrange your inspection today!

Description:
SOLD BY MATTHEW RINGERI!
CRANBOURNE EAST:This fine family home allows the lucky new purchaser to move into the ever popular Hunt Club Estate.
This quality built home featuring 4 spacious bedrooms and open study, the master suite is complete with a WIR and a FES, whilst bedrooms 2, 3 and 4 all have built in robes and are near to the family bathroom with separate bath and shower facilities!
The hostess kitchen is the central hub of the home and offers ample cupboard space, descent bench space, splash back and pantry. Stainless steel appliances including 600mm oven, gas cooktop, dishwasher and rangehood.
With 2 spacious living zones and dining area you will have no issues being short on space or entertaining year in year out, with sliding door access out to the under roof alfresco perfect for all year-round use! Added internal extras gas ducted heating, split system cooling, combination of both carpet and tiles throughout the home and blinds.
Step outside and be greeted with a block measuring app. 512m2. The spacious rear yard offers any green thumb to put their own spin on things and with an abundance of room for those with kids and pets.
The Hunt Club is a multi award winning estate offering numerous parks, wetlands, walking and bicycle paths as well as a complete range of childcare, primary (Cranbourne East Primary) and secondary schools (Cranbourne East Secondary College). Buses weave through the estate making the newly built shopping centre complete with Woolworths & Aldi easily accessible. Environmentally friendly designs are all part of the estate.
